### Application Flow
1. `load_data()` ‚Äî reads CSV, strips column names, parses Timestamp, derives `Elapsed Min`
2. Sidebar renders all user controls
3. `filtered` DataFrame is built from depth range + sample size selections
4. All charts reference `filtered` and `selected_metric`
5. Layout renders in 4 rows: Map/TS ‚Üí Depth/Corr ‚Üí Scatter/Hist ‚Üí Stats/Anomaly

