## Key Design Patterns

### METRICS Config Dict
Centralizes all per-parameter metadata to avoid repetition:
```python
METRICS = {
    'Temp C': {'label': 'Temperature', 'unit': '¬∞C', 'color': '#ff6b35'},
    ...
}
```

### PLOTLY_TEMPLATE Dict
Shared layout settings applied to every chart for visual consistency:
```python
PLOTLY_TEMPLATE = dict(
    paper_bgcolor='rgba(0,0,0,0)',
    plot_bgcolor='#071525',
    font=dict(color='#7aabcc', ...),
    ...
)
```

