## Common Issues

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `ScriptRunContext` warning | Running with `python` instead of `streamlit run` | Use `streamlit run main.py` |
| Blank map | No internet / firewall blocking tile CDN | Check connection |
| OLS trendline error | statsmodels not installed | `pip install statsmodels` |
| `KeyError` on column | Extra whitespace in CSV headers | Already handled by `.str.strip()` |
| Empty anomaly table | All data within ¬±2œÉ (normal distribution) | Expected ‚Äî no anomalies present |

